data.description: The layout of this beautiful two-story, 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is thoughtfully designed to optimize space and functionality, accommodating the needs of a larger household while offering comfort and practicality throughout. As you enter through the front door, you step into a welcoming foyer with a view straight through to the main living area, hinting at the openness and fluidity within. An open concept living room serves as the central gathering area, featuring plenty of windows for natural light and fireplace with remote start as a focal point. The kitchen is well-equipped with brand new stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, ample cabinet storage, large pantry, and a breakfast bar. The adjacent dining area provides space for family meals and casual gatherings. One of the bedrooms on the first floor can be used as a guest room or home office, providing flexibility for different needs. A full bathroom on the first floor adds convenience and accessibility. The master bedroom is a spacious retreat featuring a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. You will truly be amazed at the generous size of the bedrooms this home features. The homeowner has prepared this home move in ready with newly installed LVP throughout the main level and bathrooms, brand new carpet throughout the upper level, brand new, never used, built in microwave and range. Freshly painted throughout, each room is a blank canvas for your personal design style. The affordable HOA includes trash service and lawn maintenance. All worry set aside with the 2-10 Home Warranty that comes with the purchase! Conveniently located minutes from all essential amenities such as grocery stores, restaurants, schools, parks, and shopping centers. Minutes to I85, Sugarloaf Pkwy. and Ronald Reagan Pkwy.Preferred lender, Gina Herron with Elite Synergy Mortgage. 678-526-3563. Gina can make it happen!
